Точкові діаграми

ggplot(data = diamonds) +
  geom_point(mapping = aes(x = carat, y = price))

ggplot(diamonds) +
  geom_point(aes(carat, price))

diamonds %>% 
  ggplot() +
  geom_point(aes(carat, price))

diamonds %>% 
  ggplot() +
  geom_point(aes(carat, price, shape = cut))

diamonds %>% 
  ggplot() +
  geom_point(aes(carat, price, color = cut))

diamonds %>% 
  ggplot(aes(carat, price, color = cut)) +
  geom_point() +
  geom_smooth(method = "loess", se = FALSE)

diamonds %>% 
  ggplot(aes(carat, price, color = cut)) +
  geom_point() +
  geom_smooth(method = "loess", se = FALSE) +
  facet_grid(cut ~ .)

diamonds %>% 
  ggplot(aes(carat, price, color = cut)) +
  geom_point() +
  geom_smooth(method = "loess", se = FALSE) +
  facet_grid(~ cut)

diamonds %>% 
  ggplot(aes(carat, price, color = cut)) +
  geom_point() +
  geom_smooth(method = "loess", se = FALSE) +
  facet_grid(~ cut) +
  theme(legend.position = "none")

diamonds %>% 
  ggplot(aes(carat, price, color = cut)) +
  geom_point() +
  geom_smooth(method = "loess", se = FALSE) +
  facet_grid(~ cut) +
  theme(legend.position = "bottom")

diamonds %>% 
  ggplot(aes(carat, price, color = cut)) +
  geom_point(alpha = 0.2) +
  geom_smooth(method = "loess", se = FALSE) +
  facet_grid(~ cut) +
  theme(legend.position = "bottom")

diamonds %>% 
  ggplot(aes(cut, fill = color)) + 
  geom_bar(position = "fill") +
  geom_text(data = . %>% 
              group_by(cut, color) %>% 
              tally() %>% 
              mutate(p = (n / sum(n))) %>% 
              ungroup(),
            aes(y = p, label = scales::percent(p, accuracy = 0.01)),
            position = position_stack(vjust = 0.5),
            color = "white") + 
  theme(legend.position = "none")

diamonds %>% 
  ggplot(aes(cut)) +
  geom_bar() + 
  geom_text(data = . %>% 
              count(cut),
              aes(y = n, label = n),
            vjust = -0.25)

Гастограма та графік щільності розподілу

diamonds %>% 
  ggplot() +
  geom_histogram(aes(price))

diamonds %>% 
  ggplot() +
  geom_density(aes(price))

diamonds %>% 
  ggplot(aes(price)) +
  geom_histogram(aes(fill = cut), alpha = 0.3)

diamonds %>% 
  ggplot(aes(price, fill = clarity)) + 
  geom_density(alpha = 0.3)

Точкова зі зміщенням (для двох номінативних змінних)

diamonds %>% 
  ggplot(aes(cut, clarity, color = color)) + 
  geom_jitter(alpha = 0.2)

diamonds %>% 
  ggplot(aes(price, carat)) +
  geom_jitter(aes(color = cut, size = table), alpha = 0.2)

Box-plot

diamonds %>% 
  ggplot(aes(cut, table)) +
  geom_boxplot()

ПОБУДОВА КАРТ

Карта України

ukraine_map <- map_data("world", region = "Ukraine")

ukraine_map %>% 
  ggplot(aes(long, lat, group = "group")) + 
  geom_polygon(fill = "darkgreen") +
  coord_quickmap()

Карта України з аеропортами

ua_airports <- read_csv("https://git.io/J1do6")

ggplot() +
  geom_map(data = ukraine_map,
           map = ukraine_map,
           aes(map_id = region),
           fill = "grey75")+
  geom_point(data = ua_airports,
             aes(long, lat, color = type), size = 1) +
  coord_quickmap() + 
  theme_void()
